{"tid":1160319,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳《吸血新世紀》羅拔柏迪臣接班演蝙蝠俠","createTime":"2019-05-18T11:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T12:08:03.000Z","uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dca89b15f34510b2336700cc7b6be4775b79bfb0","tid":1160319,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/28797/117216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F28797%2F117216.jpg&h=9273452d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前報導指麥里夫斯《蝙蝠俠》搜尋年青演員飾演主角Bruce Wayne，依家人選可能已經有定案，據Variety消息稱，《吸血新世紀》英國型男羅拔柏迪臣已同電影公司簽約演出新一代蝙蝠俠。 <br />\n不過，現時有報導指羅拔柏迪臣仲未正式簽約，電影公司仍考慮緊另一大熱人選《X-Men》系列「野獸」尼古拉斯侯特。由於麥里夫斯新片主要講述蝙蝠俠早年調查離奇案件嘅故事，因此需要年青演員接替賓艾佛力嘅演出。《蝙蝠俠》定於2021年6月25日上映，但目前仍未知電影幾時開拍。"},{"pid":"e85ee6f915bd8020c6a579dced6cab656a6e729a","tid":1160319,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8cee29f5943cc37569785042b72a7e61a9e8fc","tid":1160319,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"算啦 起碼戴咗面具睇唔到佢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}